<l>ei)s o)ca/lmhn e)/mbale qermh/n:</l>
<l>h)\ dh=ta li/qon me poi/hson e)f' ou(=</l>
<l>ta\s xoiri/nas a)riqmou=si.<milestone ed="p" n="334" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2></div1>
<div1 type="Agon">
<div2 type="strophe" n="1">
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>ti/s ga/r e)sq' o( tau=ta/ s' ei(/rgwn</l>
<l n="335">ka)poklh/|wn th=| qu/ra|; le/con:</l>
<l>pro\s eu)/nous ga\r fra/seis.</l>
<milestone ed="p" n="336" unit="card"/>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="proepirrheme">
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>ou(mo\s ui(o/s. a)lla\ mh\ boa=te: kai\ ga\r tugxa/nei</l>
<l>ou(tosi\ pro/sqen kaqeu/dwn. a)ll' u(/fesqe tou= to/nou.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>tou= d' e)/fecin w)= ma/taie tau=ta dra=n se bou/letai;</l>
<l><add>kai\</add> ti/na pro/fasin e)/xwn;</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l n="340">ou)k e)a=| m' w)=ndres dika/zein ou)de\ dra=n ou)de\n kako/n,</l>
<l>a)lla/ m' eu)wxei=n e(/toimo/s e)st': e)gw\ d' ou) bou/lomai.<milestone ed="p" n="342" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="strophe" n="2">
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>tou=t' e)to/lmhs' o( miaro\s xanei=n</l>
<l n="342b">o( *dhmologokle/wn <add>o(/d',</add></l>
<l n="343">o(/ti le/geis <add>su/</add> ti peri\ tw=n new=n</l>
<l n="343b">a)lhqe/s. ou) ga\r a)/n poq'</l>
<l>ou(=tos a(nh\r tou=t' e)to/lmhsen</l>
<l n="344b">le/gein, ei)</l>
<l n="345">mh\ cunwmo/ths tis h)=n.<milestone ed="p" n="346" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="katakeleusmenos">
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l n="346">a)ll' e)k tou/twn w(/ra tina/ soi zhtei=n kainh\n e)pi/noian,</l>
<l>h(/tis se la/qra| ta)ndro\s toudi\ katabh=nai deu=ro poih/sei.<milestone ed="p" n="348" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="epirrheme">
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>ti/s a)\n ou)=n ei)/h; zhtei=q' u(mei=s, w(s pa=n <add>a)\n</add> e)/gwge poioi/hn:</l>
<l>ou(/tw kittw= dia\ tw=n sani/dwn meta\ xoiri/nhs perielqei=n.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l n="350">e)/stin o)ph\ dh=q' h(/ntin' a)\n e)/ndoqen oi(=o/s t' ei)/hs dioru/cai,</l>
<l>ei)=t' e)kdu=nai r(a/kesin krufqei\s w(/sper polu/mhtis *)odusseu/s;</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>pa/nta pe/farktai kou)k e)/stin o)ph=s ou)d' ei) se/rfw| diadu=nai.</l>
<l>a)ll' a)/llo ti dei= zhtei=n u(ma=s: o)pi/an d' ou)k e)/sti gene/sqai.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l n="354">me/mnhsai dh=q', o(/t' e)pi\ stratia=s kle/yas pote\ tou\s o)beli/skous</l>
<l>i(/eis sauto\n kata\ tou= tei/xous taxe/ws, o(/te *na/cos e(a/lw.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>oi)=d': a)lla\ ti/ tou=t'; ou)de\n ga\r tou=t' e)sti\n e)kei/nw| proso/moion.</l>
<l>h(/bwn ga\r ka)duna/mhn kle/ptein, i)/sxuo/n t' au)to\s e)mautou=,<milestone ed="p" n="358" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="pnigos">
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>kou)dei/s m' e)fu/latt', a)ll' e)ch=n moi</l>
<l>feu/gein a)dew=s. nu=n de\ cu\n o(/plois</l>
<l n="360">a)/ndres o(pli=tai diataca/menoi</l>
<l>kata\ ta\s dio/dous skopiwrou=ntai,</l>
<l>tw\ de\ du/' au)tw=n e)pi\ tai=si qu/rais</l>
<l>w(/sper me galh=n kre/a kle/yasan</l>
<l n="364">throu=sin e)/xont' o)beli/skous.<milestone ed="p" n="365" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="antistrophe" n="1">
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l n="365">a)lla\ kai\ nu=n e)kpo/rize</l>
<l>mhxanh\n o(/pws ta/xisq': e(/ws</l>
<l>ga/r, w)= meli/ttion.</l>
<milestone ed="p" n="367" unit="card"/>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="antiproepirrheme">
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>diatragei=n toi/nun kra/tisto/n e)sti/ moi to\ di/ktuon.</l>
<l>h( de/ moi *di/ktunna suggnw/mhn e)/xoi tou= diktu/ou.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>tau=ta me\n pro\s a)ndro/s e)st' a)/nontos e)s swthri/an.</l>
<l n="370">a)ll' e)/page th\n gna/qon.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>diate/trwktai tou=to/ g'. a)lla\ mh\ boa=te mhdamw=s,</l>
<l>a)lla\ thrw/mesq' o(/pws mh\ *bdelukle/wn ai)sqh/setai.<milestone ed="p" n="373" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="antistrophe" n="2">
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>mhde\n w)= ta=n de/diqi, mhde/n:</l>
<l>w(s e)gw\ tou=to/n g', e)a\n gru/ch|</l>
<l>ti, poih/sw dakei=n th\n</l>
<l n="375">kardi/an kai\ to\n peri\ yuxh=s</l>
<l>dro/mon dramei=n, i(/n' ei)dh=|</l>
<l>mh\ patei=n ta\</l>
<l>toi=n qeoi=n yhfi/smata.<milestone ed="p" n="379" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="antikatakeleusmenos">
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l n="379">a)ll' e)ca/yas dia\ th=s quri/dos to\ kalw/|dion ei)=ta kaqi/ma</l>
<l>dh/sas sauto\n kai\ th\n yuxh\n e)mplhsa/menos *diopei/qous.<milestone ed="p" n="381" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="antepirrheme">
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>a)/ge nun, h)\n ai)sqome/nw tou/tw zhth=to/n m' e)skalama=sqai</l>
<l>ka)naspasto\n poiei=n ei)/sw, ti/ poih/sete; fra/zete nuni/.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>a)munou=me/n soi to\n prinw/dh qumo\n a(/pantes kale/santes</l>
<l>w(/st' ou) dunato/n s' ei(/rgein e)/stai: toiau=ta poih/somen h(mei=s.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l n="385">dra/sw toi/nun u(mi=n pi/sunos, kai\ &mdash; manqa/net'; &mdash; h)/n ti pa/qw 'gw/,</l>
<l>a)nelo/ntes kai\ kataklau/santes qei=nai/ m' u(po\ toi=si drufa/ktois.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>ou)de\n pei/sei: mhde\n dei/sh|s. a)ll' w)= be/ltiste kaqi/ei</l>
<l>sauto\n qarrw=n ka)peuca/menos toi=si patrw/|oisi qeoi=sin.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l n="389">w)= *lu/ke de/spota, gei/twn h(/rws: su\ ga\r oi(=sper e)gw\ kexa/rhsai,</l>
<l>toi=s dakru/oisin tw=n feugo/ntwn a)ei\ kai\ toi=s o)lofurmoi=s:</l>
<l>w)/|khsas gou=n e)pi/thdes i)w\n e)ntau=q' i(/na tau=t' a)krow=|o,</l>
<l>ka)boulh/qhs mo/nos h(rw/wn para\ to\n kla/onta kaqh=sqai.</l>
<l>e)le/hson kai\ sw=son nuni\ to\n sautou= plhsio/xwron:</l>
<l>kou) mh/ pote/ sou para\ ta\s ka/nnas ou)rh/sw mhd' a)popa/rdw.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l n="395">ou(=tos e)gei/rou.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*canqi/as</speaker>
<l part="M">ti/ to\ pra=gm';</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">w(/sper fwnh/ me/ tis e)gkeku/klwtai.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*canqi/as</speaker>
<l>mw=n o( ge/rwn ph| diadu/etai <add>au)=</add>;</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">ma\ *di/' ou) dh=t', a)lla\ kaqima=|</l>
<l>au(to\n dh/sas.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*canqi/as</speaker>
<l part="M">w)= miarw/tate ti/ poiei=s; ou) mh\ katabh/sei;</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>a)na/bain' a)nu/sas kata\ th\n e(te/ran kai\ tai=sin fulla/si pai=e,</l>
<l>h)/n pws pru/mnhn a)nakrou/shtai plhgei\s tai=s ei)resiw/nais.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>ou) cullh/yesq' o(po/soisi di/kai th=tes me/llousin e)/sesqai,</l>
<l>w)= *smikuqi/wn kai\ *teisia/dh kai\ *xrh/mwn kai\ *fere/deipne;</l>
<l>po/te d', ei) mh\ nu=n, e)parh/cete/ moi, pri/n m' ei)/sw ma=llon a)/gesqai;<milestone ed="p" n="403" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2></div1>
<div1 type="Choral">
<div2 type="strophe">
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>ei)pe/ moi ti/ me/llomen kinei=n e)kei/nhn th\n xolh/n,</l>
<l n="404">h(/nper, h(ni/k' a)/n tis h(mw=n o)rgi/sh| th\n sfhkia/n;</l>
<l>nu=n e)kei=no nu=n e)kei=no</l>
<l>tou)cu/qumon, w(=| kolazo/mesqa,</l>
<l>ke/ntron &dagger;e)nte/tat' o)cu/&dagger;.</l>
<l>a)lla\ qai)ma/tia balo/ntes w(s ta/xista, paidi/a,</l>
<l>qei=te kai\ boa=te, kai\ *kle/wni tau=t' a)gge/llete,</l>
<l n="410">kai\ keleu/et' au)to\n h(/kein</l>
<l>w(s e)p' a)/ndra miso/polin</l>
<l>o)/nta ka)polou/menon, o(/ti</l>
<l>to/nde lo/gon e)sfe/rei,</l>
<l>mh\ dika/zein di/kas.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l n="415">w)=gaqoi\ to\ pra=gm' a)kou/sat', a)lla\ mh\ kekra/gete.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>nh\ *di/' e)s to\n ou)rano/n g'.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">w(s tou=d' e)gw\ ou) meqh/somai.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>tau=ta dh=t' ou) deina\ kai\ turanni/s e)stin e)mfanh/s;</l>
<l>w)= po/lis kai\ *qew/rou qeoisexqri/a,</l>
<l>kei)/ tis a)/llos proe/sthken h(mw=n ko/lac.<milestone ed="p" n="420" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="trochees">
<sp>
<speaker>*canqi/as</speaker>
<l n="420">*(hra/kleis kai\ ke/ntr' e)/xousin. ou)x o(ra=|s w)= de/spota;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>oi(=s g' a)pw/lesan *fi/lippon e)n di/kh| to\n *gorgi/ou.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>kai\ se/ g' au)toi=s e)colou=men: a)lla\ pa=s e)pi/strefe</l>
<l>deu=ro ka)cei/ras to\ ke/ntron ei)=t' e)p' au)to\n i(/eso,</l>
<l>custalei\s eu)/taktos o)rgh=s kai\ me/nous e)mplh/menos,</l>
<l n="425">w(s a)\n eu)= ei)dh=| to\ loipo\n smh=nos oi(=on w)/rgisen.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*canqi/as</speaker>
<l>tou=to me/ntoi deino\n h)/dh nh\ *di/', ei) maxou/meqa:</l>
<l>w(s e)/gwg' au)tw=n o(rw=n de/doika ta\s e)gkentri/das.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>a)ll' a)fi/ei to\n a)/ndr': ei) de\ mh/, fh/m' e)gw\</l>
<l>ta\s xelw/nas makariei=n se tou= de/rmatos.<milestone ed="p" n="430" unit="card"/></l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l n="430">ei)=a/ nun w)= cundikastai\ sfh=kes o)cuka/rdioi,</l>
<l>oi( me\n e)s to\n prwkto\n au)tw=n e)spe/tesq' w)rgisme/noi,</l>
<l>oi( de\ tw)fqalmw\ ku/klw| kentei=te kai\ tou\s daktu/lous.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>w)= *mi/da kai\ *fru\c boh/qei deu=ro kai\ *masintu/a,</l>
<l>kai\ la/besqe toutoui\ kai\ mh\ meqh=sqe mhdeni/:</l>
<l n="435">ei) de\ mh/, 'n pe/dais paxei/ais ou)de\n a)risth/sete.</l>
<l>w(s e)gw\ pollw=n a)kou/sas oi)=da qri/wn to\n yo/fon.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>ei) de\ mh\ tou=ton meqh/seis, e)/n ti/ soi pagh/setai.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>w)= *ke/kroy h(/rws a)/nac ta\ pro\s podw=n *drakonti/dh,</l>
<l>periora=|s ou(/tw m' u(p' a)ndrw=n barba/rwn xeirou/menon,</l>
<l n="440">ou(\s e)gw\ 'di/daca kla/ein te/ttar' e)s th\n xoi/nika;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>ei)=ta dh=t' ou) po/ll' e)/nesti deina\ tw=| gh/ra| kaka/;</l>
<l>dhladh/: kai\ nu=n ge tou/tw to\n palaio\n despo/thn</l>
<l>pro\s bi/an xeirou=sin, ou)de\n tw=n pa/lai memnhme/noi</l>
<l>difqerw=n ka)cwmi/dwn, a(\s ou(=tos au)toi=s h)mpo/la,</l>
<l n="445">kai\ kuna=s: kai\ tou\s po/das xeimw=nos o)/ntos w)fe/lei,</l>
<l>w(/ste mh\ r(igw=n e(ka/stot': a)lla\ tou/tois g' ou)k e)/ni</l>
<l>ou)d' e)n o)fqalmoi=sin ai)dw\s tw=n palaiw=n e)mba/dwn.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>ou)k a)fh/seis ou)de\ nuni/ m' w)= ka/kiston qhri/on,</l>
<l>ou)d' a)namnhsqei\s o(/q' eu(rw\n tou\s bo/trus kle/ptonta/ se</l>
<l n="450">prosagagw\n pro\s th\n e)la/an e)ce/deir' eu)= ka)ndrikw=s,</l>
<l>w(/ste se zhlwto\n ei)=nai; su\ d' a)xa/ristos h)=sq' a)/ra.</l>
<l>a)ll' a)/nes me kai\ su\ kai\ su/, pri\n to\n ui(o\n e)kdramei=n.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>a)lla\ tou/twn me\n ta/x' h(mi=n dw/seton kalh\n di/khn,</l>
<l>ou)ke/t' e)s makra\n i(/n' ei)dh=q' oi(=o/s e)st' a)ndrw=n tro/pos</l>
<l n="455">o)cuqu/mwn kai\ dikai/wn kai\ blepo/ntwn ka/rdama.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>pai=e pai)= w)= *canqi/a tou\s sfh=kas a)po\ th=s oi)ki/as.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*canqi/as</speaker>
<l>a)lla\ drw= tou=t': a)lla\ kai\ su\ tu=fe pollw=| tw=| kapnw=|.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*swsi/as</speaker>
<l>ou)xi\ sou=sq'; ou)k e)s ko/rakas; ou)k a)/pite; pai=e tw=| cu/lw|.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*canqi/as</speaker>
<l>kai\ su\ prosqei\s *ai)sxi/nhn e)/ntufe to\n *sellarti/ou.</l>
<l n="460">a)=r' e)me/llome/n poq' u(ma=s a)posobh/sein tw=| xro/nw|.<milestone ed="p" n="461" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="antistrophe">
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>a)lla\ ma\ *di/' ou) r(a|di/ws ou(/tws a)\n au)tou\s die/fuges,</l>
<l>ei)/per e)/tuxon tw=n melw=n tw=n *filokle/ous bebrwko/tes.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>a)=ra dh=t' ou)k au)ta\ dh=la</l>
<l>toi=s pe/nhsin, h( turanni\s</l>
<l n="465">&dagger;w(s la/qra| g' e)la/nqan' u(piou=sa/ me,&dagger;</l>
<l>ei) su/ g' w)= po/nw| po/nhre kai\ komhtamuni/a</l>
<l>tw=n no/mwn h(ma=s a)pei/rgeis w(=n e)/qhken h( po/lis,</l>
<l>ou)/te tin' e)/xwn pro/fasin</l>
<l>ou)/te lo/gon eu)tra/pelon,</l>
<l n="470">au)to\s a)/rxwn mo/nos;</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>e)/sq' o(/pws a)/neu ma/xhs kai\ th=s katocei/as boh=s</l>
<l>e)s lo/gous e)/lqoimen a)llh/loisi kai\ diallaga/s;</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>sou)s lo/gous w)= miso/dhme kai\ monarxi/as e)rasta/,</l>
<l n="475">kai\ cunw\n *brasi/da| kai\ forw=n kra/speda</l>
<l>stemma/twn th/n q' u(ph/nhn a)/kouron tre/fwn;<milestone ed="p" n="477" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="trochees">
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>nh\ *di/' h)= moi krei=tton e)ksth=nai to\ para/pan tou= patro\s</l>
<l>ma=llon h)\ kakoi=s tosou/tois naumaxei=n o(shme/rai.</l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="trochees">
<sp>
<speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l n="480">ou)de\ mh\n ou)d' e)n seli/nw| sou)sti\n ou)d' e)n phga/nw|:</l>
<l>tou=to ga\r parembalou=men tw=n trixoini/kwn e)pw=n.</l>
<l>a)lla\ nu=n me\n ou)de\n a)lgei=s, a)ll' o(/tan cunh/goros</l>
<l>tau)ta\ tau=ta sou katantlh=| kai\ cunwmo/tas kalh=|.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>a)=r' a)\n w)= pro\s tw=n qew=n u(mei=s a)pallaxqei=te/ mou;</l>
<l n="485">h)\ de/doktai/ moi de/resqai kai\ de/rein di' h(me/ras;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>ou)de/pote/ g', ou)x e(/ws a)/n ti/ mou loipo\n h)=|,</l>
<l>o(/stis h(mw=n e)pi\ turanni/d' w(=d' e)sta/lhs.<milestone ed="p" n="488" unit="card"/></l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>w(s a(/panq' u(mi=n turanni/s e)sti kai\ cunwmo/tai,</l>
<l>h)/n te mei=zon h)/n t' e)/latton pra=gma/ tis kathgorh=|,</l>
<l n="490">h(=s e)gw\ ou)k h)/kousa tou)/nom' ou)de\ penth/kont' e)tw=n:</l>
<l>nu=n de\ pollw=| tou= tari/xous e)sti\n a)ciwte/ra,</l>
<l>w(/ste kai\ dh\ tou)/nom' au)th=s e)n a)gora=| kuli/ndetai.</l>
<l>h)\n me\n w)nh=tai/ tis o)rfw\s membra/das de\ mh\ 'qe/lh|,</l>
<l>eu)qe/ws ei)/rhx' o( pwlw=n plhsi/on ta\s membra/das:</l>
<l n="495">'ou(=tos o)ywnei=n e)/oix' a(/nqrwpos e)pi\ turanni/di.'</l>
<l>h)\n de\ gh/teion prosaith=| tai=s a)fu/ais h(/dusma/ ti,</l>
<l>h( laxano/pwlis parable/yasa/ fhsi qate/rw|:</l>
<l>&lsquo;ei)pe/ moi, gh/teion ai)tei=s: po/teron e)pi\ turanni/di,</l>
<l>h)\ nomi/zeis ta\s *)aqh/nas soi\ fe/rein h(du/smata;&rsquo;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*canqi/as</speaker>
<l n="500">ka)me/ g' h( po/rnh xqe\s ei)selqo/nta th=s meshmbri/as,</l>
<l>o(/ti kelhti/sai 'ke/leuon, o)cuqumhqei=sa/ moi</l>
<l>h)/ret' ei) th\n *(ippi/ou kaqi/stamai turanni/da.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>tau=ta ga\r tou/tois a)kou/ein h(de)/, ei) kai\ nu=n e)gw\</l>
<l>to\n pate/r' o(/ti bou/lomai tou/twn a)pallaxqe/nta tw=n</l>
<l n="505">o)rqrofoitosukofantodikotalaipw/rwn tro/pwn</l>
<l>zh=n bi/on gennai=on w(/sper *mo/ruxos, ai)ti/an e)/xw</l>
<l>tau=ta dra=n cunwmo/ths w)\n kai\ fronw=n turannika/.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>nh\ *di/' e)n di/kh| g': e)gw\ ga\r ou)d' a)\n o)rni/qwn ga/la</l>
<l>a)nti\ tou= bi/ou la/boim' a)\n ou(= me nu=n a)posterei=s:</l>
<l n="510">ou)de\ xai/rw bati/sin ou)d' e)gxe/lesin, a)ll' h(/dion a)/n</l>
<l>diki/dion smikro\n fa/goim' a)\n e)n lopa/di pepnigme/non.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>nh\ *di/' ei)qi/sqhs ga\r h(/desqai toiou/tois pra/gmasin:</l>
<l>a)ll' e)a\n sigw=n a)na/sxh| kai\ ma/qh|s a(gw\ le/gw,</l>
<l>a)nadida/cein oi)/omai/ s' w(s pa/nta tau=q' a(marta/neis.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l n="515">e)camarta/nw dika/zwn;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">katagelw/menos me\n ou)=n</l>
<l>ou)k e)pai+eis u(p' a)ndrw=n, ou(\s su\ mo/non ou) proskunei=s.</l>
<l>a)lla\ douleu/wn le/lhqas.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">pau=e doulei/an le/gwn,</l>
<l>o(/stis a)/rxw tw=n a(pa/ntwn.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">ou) su/ g', a)ll' u(phretei=s</l>
<l>oi)o/menos a)/rxein: e)pei\ di/dacon h(ma=s w)= pa/ter,</l>
<l n="520">h(/tis h( timh/ 'sti/ soi karpoume/nw| th\n *(ella/da.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>pa/nu ge, kai\ tou/toisi/ g' e)pitre/yai 'qe/lw.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">kai\ mh\n e)gw/.</l>
<l>a)/fete/ nun a(/pantes au)to/n.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">kai\ ci/fos ge/ moi do/te.</l>
<l>h)\n ga\r h(tthqw= le/gwn sou, peripesou=mai tw=| ci/fei.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>ei)pe/ moi, ti/ d' h)/n, to\ dei=na, th=| diai/th| mh\ 'mme/nh|s;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l n="525">mhde/pote pi/oim' a)kra/tou misqo\n a)gaqou= dai/monos.<milestone ed="p" n="526" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2></div1>
<div1 type="Agon">
<div2 type="strophe">
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>nu=n dh\ to\n e)k qh)mete/rou</l>
<l>gumnasi/ou dei= ti le/gein</l>
<l>kaino/n, o(/pws fanh/sei &mdash;</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>e)negka/tw moi deu=ro th\n ki/sthn tis w(s ta/xista.</l>
<l n="530">a)ta\r fanei= poi=o/s tis w)/n, h)\n tau=ta parakeleu/h|;</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>mh\ kata\ to\n neani/an</l>
<l>tondi\ le/gwn. o(ra=|s ga\r w(/s</l>
<l>soi me/gas e)sti\n a(gw\n</l>
<l>kai\ peri\ tw=n a(pa/ntwn,</l>
<l n="535">ei)/per, o(\ mh\ ge/noiq', ou(=to/s</l>
<l><add>s'</add> e)qe/lei krath=sai.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>kai\ mh\n o(/s' a)\n le/ch| g' a(plw=s mnhmo/suna gra/yomai 'gw/.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>ti/ ga\r fa/q' u(mei=s, h)\n o(di/ me tw=| lo/gw| krath/sh|;</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l n="540">ou)ke/ti presbutw=n o)/xlos</l>
<l>xrh/simos e)/st' ou)d' a)karh=:</l>
<l>skwpto/menoi d' e)n tai=s o(doi=s</l>
<l>qallofo/roi kalou/meq', a)ntwmosiw=n</l>
<l n="545">kelu/fh.<milestone ed="p" n="546" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="katakeleusmenos">
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l n="546">a)ll' w)= peri\ th=s pa/shs me/llwn basilei/as a)ntilogh/sein</l>
<l>th=s h(mete/ras, nuni\ qarrw=n pa=san glw=ttan basa/nize.<milestone ed="p" n="548" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="epirrheme">
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>kai\ mh\n eu)qu/s g' a)po\ balbi/dwn peri\ th=s a)rxh=s a)podei/cw</l>
<l>th=s h(mete/ras w(s ou)demia=s h(/ttwn e)sti\n basilei/as.</l>
<l n="550">ti/ ga\r eu)/daimon kai\ makaristo\n ma=llon nu=n e)sti\ dikastou=,</l>
<l>h)\ truferw/teron h)\ deino/teron zw=|on, kai\ tau=ta ge/rontos;</l>
<l>o(\n prw=ta me\n e(/rpont' e)c eu)nh=s throu=s' e)pi\ toi=si drufa/ktois</l>
<l>a)/ndres mega/loi kai\ tetraph/xeis: ka)/peit' eu)qu\s prosio/nti</l>
<l>e)mba/llei moi th\n xei=r' a(palh\n tw=n dhmosi/wn keklofui=an:</l>
<l n="555">i(keteu/ousi/n q' u(poku/ptontes th\n fwnh\n oi)ktroxoou=ntes:</l>
<l>'oi)/ktiro/n m' w)= pa/ter, ai)tou=mai/ s', ei) kau)to\s pw/poq' u(fei/lou</l>
<l>a)rxh\n a)/rcas h)\ 'pi\ stratia=s toi=s cussi/tois a)gora/zwn:'</l>
<l>o(\s e)/m' ou)d' a)\n zw=nt' h)/|dein ei) mh\ dia\ th\n prote/ran a)po/fucin.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>touti\ peri\ tw=n a)ntibolou/ntwn e)/stw to\ mnhmo/suno/n moi.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l n="560">ei)=t' ei)selqw\n a)ntibolhqei\s kai\ th\n o)rgh\n a)pomorxqei\s</l>
<l>e)/ndon tou/twn w(=n a)\n fa/skw pa/ntwn ou)de\n pepoi/hka,</l>
<l>a)ll' a)krow=mai pa/sas fwna\s i(e/ntwn ei)s a)po/fucin.</l>
<l>fe/r' i)/dw, ti/ ga\r ou)k e)/stin a)kou=sai qw/peum' e)ntau=qa dikasth=|;</l>
<l>oi( me/n g' a)pokla/ontai peni/an au(tw=n kai\ prostiqe/asi</l>
<l n="565">kaka\ pro\s toi=s ou)=sin, &dagger; e(/ws a)niw=n a)\n i)sw/sh| toi=sin e)moi=sin: &dagger;</l>
<l>oi( de\ le/gousin mu/qous h(mi=n, oi( d' *ai)sw/pou ti ge/loion:</l>
<l>oi( de\ skw/ptous', i(/n' e)gw\ gela/sw kai\ to\n qumo\n kataqw=mai.</l>
<l>ka)\n mh\ tou/tois a)napeiqw/mesqa, ta\ paida/ri' eu)qu\s a)ne/lkei</l>
<l>ta\s qhlei/as kai\ tou\s ui(ei=s th=s xeiro/s, e)gw\ d' a)krow=mai:</l>
<l n="570">ta\ de\ sugku/yanq' a(/ma blhxa=tai: ka)/peiq' o( path\r u(pe\r au)tw=n</l>
<l>w(/sper qeo\n a)ntibolei= me tre/mwn th=s eu)qu/nhs a)polu=sai:</l>
<l><q>ei) me\n xai/reis a)rno\s fwnh=|, paido\s fwnh\n e)leh/sais:</q></l>
<l>ei) d' au)= toi=s xoiridi/ois xai/rw, qugatro\s fwnh=| me piqe/sqai.</l>
<l>xh)mei=s au)tw=| to/te th=s o)rgh=s o)li/gon to\n ko/llop' a)nei=men.</l>
<l n="575">a)=r' ou) mega/lh tou=t' e)/st' a)rxh\ kai\ tou= plou/tou kataxh/nh;<milestone ed="p" n="576" unit="card"/></l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>deu/teron au)= sou touti\ gra/fomai, th\n tou= plou/tou kataxh/nhn:</l>
<l>kai\ ta)gaqa/ moi me/mnhs' a(/xeis fa/skwn th=s *(ella/dos a)/rxein.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>pai/dwn toi/nun dokimazome/nwn ai)doi=a pa/resti qea=sqai.</l>
<l>ka)\n *oi)/agros ei)se/lqh| feu/gwn, ou)k a)pofeu/gei pri\n a)\n h(mi=n</l>
<l n="580">e)k th=s *nio/bhs ei)/ph| r(h=sin th\n kalli/sthn a)pole/cas.</l>
<l>ka)\n au)lhth/s ge di/khn nika=|, tau/ths h(mi=n e)pi/xeira</l>
<l>e)n forbeia=| toi=si dikastai=s e)/codon hu)/lhs' a)piou=si.</l>
<l>ka)\n a)poqnh/|skwn o( path/r tw| dw=| katalei/pwn pai=d' e)pi/klhron,</l>
<l>kla/ein h(mei=s makra\ th\n kefalh\n ei)po/ntes th=| diaqh/kh|</l>
<l n="585">kai\ th=| ko/gxh| th=| pa/nu semnw=s toi=s shmei/oisin e)pou/sh|,</l>
<l>e)/domen tau/thn o(/stis a)\n h(ma=s a)ntibolh/sas a)napei/sh|.</l>
<l>kai\ tau=t' a)nupeu/qunoi drw=men, tw=n d' a)/llwn ou)demi)/ a)rxh/.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>touti\ ga/r toi semno/n, tou/twn w(=n ei)/rhkas makari/zw:</l>
<l>th=s d' e)piklh/rou th\n diaqh/khn a)dikei=s a)nakogxulia/zwn.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l n="590">e)/ti d' h( boulh\ xw) dh=mos o(/tan kri=nai me/ga pra=gm' a)porh/sh|</l>
<l>e)yh/fistai tou\s a)dikou=ntas toi=si dikastai=s paradou=nai:</l>
<l>ei)=t' *eu)/aqlos xw) me/gas ou(=tos *kolakw/numos a)spidapoblh\s</l>
<l>ou)xi\ prodw/sein h(ma=s fasi/n, peri\ tou= plh/qous de\ maxei=sqai.</l>
<l>ka)n tw=| dh/mw| gnw/mhn ou)dei\s pw/pot' e)ni/khsen, e)a\n mh\</l>
<l>ei)/ph| ta\ dikasth/ri' a)fei=nai prw/tista mi/an dika/santas:</l>
<l n="596">au)to\s de\ *kle/wn o( kekracida/mas mo/non h(ma=s ou) peritrw/gei,</l>
<l>a)lla\ fula/ttei dia\ xeiro\s e)/xwn kai\ ta\s mui/as a)pamu/nei.</l>
<l>su\ de\ to\n pate/r' ou)d' o(tiou=n tou/twn to\n sautou= pw/pot' e)/drasas.</l>
<l>a)lla\ *qe/wros, kai/tou)sti\n a)nh\r *eu)fhmi/ou ou)de\n e)la/ttwn,</l>
<l n="600">to\n sfo/ggon e)/xwn e)k th=s leka/nhs ta)mba/di' h(mw=n perikwnei=.</l>
<l>ske/yai m' a)po\ tw=n a)gaqw=n oi(/wn a)poklh/|eis kai\ kateru/keis,</l>
<l>h(\n doulei/an ou)=san e)/faskes kai\ u(phresi/an a)podei/cein.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>e)/mplhso le/gwn: pa/ntws ga/r toi pau/sei pote\ ka)nafanh/sei</l>
<l>prwkto\s loutrou= perigigno/menos th=s a)rxh=s th=s perise/mnou.<milestone ed="p" n="605" unit="card"/></l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l n="605">o(\ de/ g' h(/diston tou/twn e)sti\n pa/ntwn, ou(= 'gw\ 'pelelh/smhn,</l>
<l>o(/tan oi)/kad' i)/w to\n misqo\n e)/xwn, ka)/peiq' h(/konq' a(/ma pa/ntes</l>
<l>a)spa/zwntai dia\ ta)rgu/rion, kai\ prw=ta me\n h( quga/thr me</l>
<l>a)poni/zh| kai\ tw\ po/d' a)lei/fh| kai\ prosku/yasa filh/sh|</l>
<l>kai\ pappi/zous' a(/ma th=| glw/tth| <add>to\</add> triw/bolon e)kkalama=tai,</l>
<l n="610">kai\ to\ gu/naio/n m' u(poqwpeu=san fusth\n ma=zan prosene/gkh|,</l>
<l>ka)/peita kaqezome/nh par' e)moi\ prosanagka/zh|, 'fa/ge touti/,</l>
<l>e)/ntrage touti/:' tou/toisin e)gw\ ga/numai, kou) mh/ me deh/sh|</l>
<l>e)s se\ ble/yai kai\ to\n tami/an, o(po/t' a)/riston paraqh/sei</l>
<l>katarasa/menos kai\ tonqoru/sas. a)ll' h)\n mh/ moi taxu\ ma/ch|,</l>
<l>ta/de ke/kthmai pro/blhma kakw=n, skeuh\n bele/wn a)lewrh/n.</l>
<l n="616">ka)\n oi)=no/n moi mh\ 'gxh=|s su\ piei=n, to\n o)/non to/nd' e)skeko/mismai</l>
<l>oi)/nou mesto/n, ka)=|t' e)gxe/omai kli/nas: ou(=tos de\ kexhnw\s</l>
<l>brwmhsa/menos tou= sou= di/nou me/ga kai\ stra/tion kate/parden.</l>
<l n="620">a)=r' ou) mega/lhn a)rxh\n a)/rxw kai\ tou= *dio\s ou)de\n e)la/ttw,<milestone ed="p" n="621" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="pnigos">
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>o(/stis a)kou/w tau)/q' a(/per o( *zeu/s;</l>
<l>h)\n gou=n h(mei=s qorubh/swmen,</l>
<l>pa=s ti/s fhsin tw=n pario/ntwn,</l>
<l>&lsquo;oi(=on bronta=| to\ dikasth/rion,</l>
<l n="625">w)= *zeu= basileu=.&rsquo;</l>
<l>ka)\n a)stra/yw, poppu/zousin</l>
<l>ka)gkexo/dasi/n m' oi( ploutou=ntes</l>
<l>kai\ pa/nu semnoi/.</l>
<l>kai\ su\ de/doika/s me ma/list' au)to/s:</l>
<l>nh\ th\n *dh/mhtra de/doikas, e)gw\ d'</l>
<l n="630">a)poloi/mhn ei)/ se de/doika.<milestone ed="p" n="631" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="antistrophe">
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>ou)pw/poq' ou(/tw kaqarw=s</l>
<l>ou)deno\s h)kou/samen ou)de\</l>
<l>cunetw=s le/gontos.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>ou)/k, a)ll' e)rh/mas w)/|eq' ou(/tw r(a|di/ws trugh/sein.</l>
<l n="635">kalw=s ga\r h)/|dein w(s e)gw\ tau/th| kra/tisto/s ei)mi.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>w(s d' e)pi\ pa/nt' e)lh/luqen</l>
<l>kou)de\n parh=lqen, w(/st' e)/gwg'</l>
<l>hu)cano/mhn a)kou/wn,</l>
<l>ka)n maka/rwn dika/zein</l>
<l n="640">au)to\s e)/doca nh/sois,</l>
<l>h(do/menos le/gonti.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>w(s ou(=tos h)/dh skordina=tai ka)/stin ou)k e)n au(tou=.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>h)= mh\n e)gw/ se th/meron sku/th ble/pein poih/sw.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>dei= de/ se pantoi/as ple/kein</l>
<l n="645">ei)s a)po/fucin pala/mas.</l>
<l>th\n ga\r e)mh\n o)rgh\n pepa=nai</l>
<l>xalepo\n <add>neani/a|</add></l>
<l>mh\ pro\s e)mou= le/gonti.</l>
<milestone ed="p" n="648" unit="card"/>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="antikatakeleusmenos">
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l n="648">pro\s tau=ta mu/lhn a)gaqh\n w(/ra zhtei=n soi kai\ neo/kopton,</l>
<l>h)\n mh/ ti le/gh|s, h(/tis dunath\ to\n e)mo\n qumo\n katerei=cai.<milestone ed="p" n="650" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="antepirrheme">
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l n="650">xalepo\n me\n kai\ deinh=s gnw/mhs kai\ mei/zonos h)\ 'pi\ trugw|doi=s</l>
<l>i)a/sasqai no/son a)rxai/an e)n th=| po/lei e)ntetokui=an.</l>
<l>a)ta\r w)= pa/ter h(me/tere *kroni/dh &mdash;</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">pau=sai kai\ mh\ pate/rize.</l>
<l>ei) mh\ ga\r o(/pws douleu/w 'gw/, touti\ taxe/ws me dida/ceis,</l>
<l>ou)k e)/stin o(/pws ou)xi\ teqnh/ceis, ka)\n xrh=| spla/gxnwn m' a)pe/xesqai.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l n="655">a)kro/asai/ nun w)= pappi/dion xala/sas o)li/gon to\ me/twpon:</l>
<l>kai\ prw=ton me\n lo/gisai fau/lws, mh\ yh/fois a)ll' a)po\ xeiro/s,</l>
<l>to\n fo/ron h(mi=n a)po\ tw=n po/lewn sullh/bdhn to\n prosio/nta:</l>
<l>ka)/cw tou/tou ta\ te/lh xwri\s kai\ ta\s polla\s e(katosta/s,</l>
<l>prutanei=a me/tall' a)gora\s lime/nas mesqou\s kai\ dhmio/prata.</l>
<l n="660">tou/twn plh/rwma ta/lant' e)ggu\s disxi/lia gi/gnetai h(mi=n.</l>
<l>a)po\ tou/tou nun kata/qes misqo\n toi=si dikastai=s e)niautou=</l>
<l>e(\c xilia/sin, kou)/pw plei/ous e)n th=| xw/ra| kate/nasqen,</l>
<l>gi/gnetai h(mi=n e(kato\n dh/pou kai\ penth/konta ta/lanta.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>ou)d' h( deka/th tw=n prosio/ntwn h(mi=n a)/r' e)gi/gneq' o( misqo/s.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l n="665">ma\ *di/' ou) me/ntoi.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">kai\ poi= tre/petai dh\ 'peita ta\ xrh/mata ta)/lla;</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>e)s tou/tous tou\s &lsquo;ou)xi\ prodw/sw to\n *)aqhnai/wn kolosurto/n,</l>
<l>a)lla\ maxou=mai peri\ tou= plh/qous a)ei/.&rsquo; su\ ga\r w)= pa/ter au)tou\s</l>
<l>a)/rxein ai(rei= sautou= tou/tois toi=s r(hmati/ois peripefqei/s.</l>
<l>ka)=|q' ou(=toi me\n dwrodokou=sin kata\ penth/konta ta/lanta</l>
<l n="670">a)po\ tw=n po/lewn e)papeilou=ntes toiauti\ ka)nafobou=ntes,</l>
<l><q>dw/sete to\n fo/ron, h)\ bronth/sas th\n po/lin u(mw=n a)natre/yw.</q></l>
<l>su\ de\ th=s a)rxh=s a)gapa=|s th=s sh=s tou\s a)rgelo/fous peritrw/gwn.</l>
<l>oi( de\ cu/mmaxoi w(s h)/|sqhntai to\n me\n su/rfaka to\n a)/llon</l>
<l>e)k khqari/on lagarizo/menon kai\ tragalizonta to\ mhde/n,</l>
<l n="675">se\ me\n h(gou=ntai *ko/nnou yh=fon, tou/toisi de\ dwroforou=sin</l>
<l>u(/rxas oi)=non da/pidas turo\n me/li sh/sama proskefa/laia</l>
<l>fia/las xlani/das stefa/nous o(/rmous e)kpw/mata plouqugiei/an:</l>
<l>soi\ d' w(=n a)/rxeis, polla\ me\n e)n gh=| polla\ d' e)f' u(gra=| pituleu/sas,</l>
<l>ou)dei\s ou)de\ skoro/dou kefalh\n toi=s e(yhtoi=si di/dwsin.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l n="680">ma\ *di/' a)lla\ par' *eu)xari/dou kau)to\s trei=s g' a)/gliqas mete/pemya.</l>
<l>a)ll' au)th/n moi th\n doulei/an ou)k a)pofai/nwn a)poknai/eis.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>ou) ga\r mega/lh doulei/a 'sti\n tou/tous me\n a(/pantas e)n a)rxai=s</l>
<l>au)tou/s t' ei)=nai kai\ tou\s ko/lakas tou\s tou/twn misqoforou=ntas;</l>
<l>soi\ d' h)/n tis dw=| tou\s trei=s o)bolou/s, a)gapa=|s: ou(\s au)to\s e)lau/nwn</l>
<l n="685">kai\ pezomaxw=n kai\ poliorkw=n e)kth/sw polla\ ponh/tas.</l>
<l>kai\ pro\s tou/tois e)pitatto/menos foita=|s, o(\ ma/lista/ m' a)pa/gxei,</l>
<l>o(/tan ei)selqo\n meira/kio/n soi kata/pugon, *xaire/ou ui(o/s,</l>
<l>w(di\ diaba\s diakinhqei\s tw=| sw/mati kai\ truferanqei/s,</l>
<l>h(/kein ei)/ph| prw\| ka)n w(/ra| dika/sonq', w(s o(/stis a)\n u(mw=n</l>
<l n="690">u(/steros e)/lqh| tou= shmei/ou, to\ triw/bolon ou) komiei=tai:</l>
<l>au)to\s de\ fe/rei to\ sunhgoriko\n draxmh/n, ka)\n u(/steros e)/lqh|:</l>
<l>kai\ koinwnw=n tw=n a)rxo/ntwn e(te/rw| tini\ tw=n meq' e(autou=,</l>
<l>h)/n ti/s ti didw=| tw=n feugo/ntwn, cunqe/nte to\ pra=gma du/' o)/nte</l>
<l>e)spouda/katon, ka)=|q' w(s pri/onq' o( me\n e(/lkei o( d' a)ntene/dwke:</l>
<l n="695">su\ de\ xaska/zeis to\n kwlakre/thn, to\ de\ pratto/meno/n se le/lhqen.<milestone ed="p" n="696" unit="card"/></l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>tauti/ me poiou=s'; oi)/moi ti/ le/geis; w(/s mou to\n qi=na tara/tteis,</l>
<l>kai\ to\n nou=n mou prosa/geis ma=llon, kou)k oi)=d' o(/ ti xrh=ma/ me poiei=s.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>ske/yai toi/nun w(s e)co/n soi ploutei=n kai\ toi=sin a(/pasin</l>
<l>u(po\ tw=n a)ei\ dhmizo/ntwn ou)k oi)=d' o(/ph| e)gkeku/klhsai,</l>
<l n="700">o(/stis po/lewn a)/rxwn plei/stwn a)po\ tou= *po/ntou me/xri *sardou=s</l>
<l>ou)k a)polau/eis plh\n tou=q' o(\ fe/reis a)karh=: kai\ tou=t' e)ri/w| soi</l>
<l>e)nsta/zousin kata\ mikro\n a)ei\ tou= zh=n e(/nex' w(/sper e)/laion.</l>
<l>bou/lontai ga/r se pe/nht' ei)=nai: kai\ tou=q' w(=n ou(/nek' e)rw= soi,</l>
<l>i(/na gignw/skh|s to\n tiqaseuth/n, ka)=|q' o(/tan ou(=to/s g' e)pisi/ch|</l>
<l n="705">e)pi\ tw=n e)xqrw=n tin' e)pirru/cas, a)gri/ws au)toi=s e)piphda=|s.</l>
<l>ei) ga\r e)bou/lonto bi/on pori/sai tw=| dh/mw|, r(a/|dion h)=n a)/n.</l>
<l>ei)si/n ge po/leis xi/liai ai(\ nu=n to\n fo/ron h(mi=n a)pa/gousi:</l>
<l>tou/twn ei)/kosin a)/ndras bo/skein ei)/ tis prose/tacen e(ka/sth|,</l>
<l>du/o muria/d' a)\n tw=n dhmotikw=n e)/zwn e)n pa=si lagw/|ois</l>
<l n="710">kai\ stefa/noisin pantodapoi=sin kai\ puria/th|,</l>
<l>a)/cia th=s gh=s a)polau/ontes kai\ tou= 'n *maraqw=ni tropai/ou.</l>
<l>nu=n d' w(/sper e)laolo/goi xwrei=q' a(/ma tw=| to\n misqo\n e)/xonti.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>oi)/moi ti/ pe/ponq'; w(s na/rkh mou kata\ th=s xeiro\s kataxei=tai,</l>
<l>kai\ to\ ci/fos ou) du/namai kate/xein, a)ll' h)/dh malqako/s ei)mi.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l n="715">a)ll' o(po/tan me\n dei/sws' au)toi/, th\n *eu)/boian dido/asin</l>
<l>u(mi=n kai\ si=ton u(fi/stantai kata\ penth/konta medi/mnous</l>
<l>poriei=n: e)/dosan d' ou)pw/pote/ soi plh\n prw/hn pe/nte medi/mnous,</l>
<l>kai\ tau=ta mo/lis ceni/as feu/gwn e)/labes kata\ xoi/nika kriqw=n.<milestone ed="p" n="719" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="antipnigos">
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>w(=n ou(/nek' e)gw/ s' a)pe/klh|on a)ei\</l>
<l n="720">bo/skein e)qe/lwn kai\ mh\ tou/tous</l>
<l>e)gxa/skein soi stomfa/zontas.</l>
<l>kai\ nu=n a)texnw=s e)qe/lw pare/xein</l>
<l>o(/ ti bou/lei soi,</l>
<l>plh\n kwlakre/tou ga/la pi/nein.<milestone ed="p" n="725" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="sphragis">
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l n="725">h)= pou sofo\s h)=n o(/stis e)/fasken, pri\n a)\n a)mfoi=n mu=qon a)kou/sh|s,</l>
<l>ou)k a)\n dika/sais. su\ ga\r ou)=n nu=n moi nika=n pollw=| dedo/khsai:</l>
<l>w(/st' h)/dh th\n o)rgh\n xala/sas tou\s ski/pwnas kataba/llw.</l>
<l>a)ll' w)= th=s h(liki/as h(mi=n th=s au)th=s sunqiasw=ta,<milestone ed="p" n="729" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2></div1>
<div1 type="Choral">
<div2 type="strophe">
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>piqou= piqou= lo/goisi, mhd' a)/frwn ge/nh|</l>
<l n="730">mhd' a)tenh\s a)/gan a)tera/mwn t' a)nh/r.</l>
<l>ei)/q' w)/fele/n moi khdemw\n h)\ cuggenh\s</l>
<l>ei)=nai/ tis o(/stis toiau=t' e)nouqe/tei.</l>
<l>soi\ de\ nu=n tis qew=n parw\n e)mfanh\s</l>
<l>cullamba/nei tou= pra/gmatos,</l>
<l n="735">kai\ dh=lo/s e)stin eu)= poiw=n:</l>
<l>su\ de\ parw\n de/xou.</l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="anapests">
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>kai\ mh\n qre/yw g' au)to\n pare/xwn</l>
<l>o(/sa presbu/th| cu/mfora, xo/ndron</l>
<l>lei/xein, xlai=nan malakh/n, sisu/ran,</l>
<l>po/rnhn, h(/tis to\ pe/os tri/yei</l>
<l n="740">kai\ th\n o)sfu=n.</l>
<l>a)ll' o(/ti siga=| kou)de\n gru/zei,</l>
<l>tou=t' ou) du/natai/ me prose/sqai.<milestone ed="p" n="743" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="antistrophe">
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>nenouqe/thken au(to\n e)s ta\ pra/gmaq', oi)=s</l>
<l>to/t' e)pemai/net': e)/gnwke ga\r a)rti/ws,</l>
<l n="745">logi/zetai/ t' e)kei=na pa/nq' a(marti/as</l>
<l>a(\ sou= keleu/ontos ou)k e)pei/qeto.</l>
<l>nu=n d' i)/sws toi=si soi=s lo/gois pei/qetai</l>
<l>kai\ swfronei= me/ntoi meqista\s</l>
<l>e)s to\ loipo\n to\n tro/pon</l>
<l n="749">piqo/meno/s te/ soi.</l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="anapests">
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>i)w/ moi/ moi.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">ou(=tos ti/ boa=|s;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l n="750">mh/ moi tou/twn mhde\n u(pisxnou=.</l>
<l>kei/nwn e)/ramai, kei=qi genoi/man,</l>
<l>i(/n' o( kh=ru/c fhsi, 'ti/s a)yh/fistos; a)nista/sqw.'</l>
<l>ka)pistai/hn e)pi\ toi=s khmoi=s</l>
<l n="755">yhfizome/nwn o( teleutai=os.</l>
<l>speu=d' w)= yuxh/. pou= moi yuxh/;</l>
<l>pa/res w)= skiera/. ma\ to\n *(hrakle/a</l>
<l>mh/ nun e)/t' e)gw\ 'n toi=si dikastai=s</l>
<l>kle/ptonta *kle/wna la/boimi.<milestone ed="p" n="760" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2></div1>
<div1 type="Episode">
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l n="760">i)/q' w)= pa/ter pro\s tw=n qew=n e)moi\ piqou=.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>ti/ soi pi/qwmai; le/g' o(/ ti bou/lei plh\n e(no/s.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>poi/ou; fe/r' i)/dw.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">tou= mh\ dika/zein. tou=to de\</l>
<l>*(/aidhs diakrinei= pro/teron h)\ 'gw\ pei/somai.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>su\ d' ou)=n, e)peidh\ tou=to kexa/rhkas poiw=n,</l>
<l n="765">e)kei=se me\n mhke/ti ba/diz', a)ll' e)nqa/de</l>
<l>au)tou= me/nwn di/kaze toi=sin oi)ke/tais.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>peri\ tou=; ti/ lhrei=s;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">tau)/q' a(/per e)kei= pra/ttetai:</l>
<l>o(/ti th\n qu/ran a)ne/w|cen h( shki\s la/qra|,</l>
<l>tau/ths e)pibolh\n yhfiei= mi/an mo/nhn.</l>
<l n="770">pa/ntws de\ ka)kei= tau=t' e)/dras e(ka/stote.</l>
<l>kai\ tau=ta me/n nun eu)lo/gws, h)\n e)ce/xh|</l>
<l>e(/lh kat' o)/rqron, h(lia/sei pro\s h(/lion:</l>
<l>e)a\n de\ nei/fh|, pro\s to\ pu=r kaqh/menos:</l>
<l>u(/ontos ei)/sei: ka)/n e)/grh| meshmbrino/s,</l>
<l n="775">ou)dei/s s' a)poklh/|sei qesmoqe/ths th=| kigkli/di.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>touti/ m' a)re/skei.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">pro\s de\ tou/tois g', h)\n di/khn</l>
<l>le/gh| makra/n tis, ou)xi\ peinw=n a)namenei=s</l>
<l>da/knwn seauto\n kai\ to\n a)pologou/menon.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>pw=s ou)=n diagignw/skein kalw=s dunh/somai</l>
<l n="780">w(/sper pro/teron ta\ pra/gmat' e)/ti masw/menos;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>pollw=| g' a)/meinon: kai\ le/getai ga\r toutogi/,</l>
<l>w(s oi( dikastai\ yeudome/nwn tw=n martu/rwn</l>
<l>mo/lis to\ pra=gm' e)/gnwsan a)namasw/menoi.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>a)na/ to/ me pei/qeis. a)ll' e)kei=n' ou)/pw le/geis,</l>
<l n="785">to\n misqo\n o(po/qen lh/yomai.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">par' e)mou=.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">kalw=s,</l>
<l>o(tih\ kat' e)mauto\n kou) meq' e(te/rou lh/yomai.</l>
<l>ai)/sxista ga/r toi/ m' h)rga/sato *lusi/stratos</l>
<l>o( skwpto/lhs. draxmh\n met' e)mou= prw/hn labw\n</l>
<l>e)lqw\n diekermati/zet' e)n toi=s i)xqu/sin,</l>
<l n="790">ka)/peit' e)ne/qhke trei=s lopi/das moi kestre/wn:</l>
<l>ka)gw\ 'ne/kay': o)bolou\s ga\r w)|o/mhn labei=n:</l>
<l>ka)=|ta bdeluxqei\s o)sfro/menos e)ce/ptusa:</l>
<l>ka)=|q' ei(=lkon au)to/n.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">o( de\ ti/ pro\s tau=t' ei)=f';</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">o(/ ti;</l>
<l>a)lektruo/nos m' e)/faske koili/an e)/xein:</l>
<l n="795"><q>taxu\ gou=n kaqe/yeis ta)rgu/rion,</q> h)= d' o(\s le/gwn.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>o(ra=|s o(/son kai\ tou=to dh=ta kerdanei=s.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>ou) pa/nu ti mikro/n. a)ll' o(/per me/lleis poi/ei.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>a)na/mene/ nun: e)gw\ de\ tau=q' h(/cw fe/rwn.<milestone ed="p" n="799" unit="card"/></l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>o(/ra to\ xrh=ma, ta\ lo/gi' w(s perai/netai.</l>
<l n="800">h)khko/h ga\r w(s *)aqhnai=oi/ pote</l>
<l>dika/soien e)pi\ tai=s oi)ki/aisi ta\s di/kas,</l>
<l>ka)n toi=s proqu/rois e)noikodomh/soi pa=s a)nh\r</l>
<l>au(tw=| dikasthri/dion mikro\n pa/nu,</l>
<l>w(/sper *(eka/taion, pantaxou= pro\ tw=n qurw=n.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l n="805">i)dou/, ti/ e)/t' e)rei=s; w(s a(/pant' e)gw\ fe/rw</l>
<l>o(/saper e)/faskon, ka)/ti pollw=| plei/ona.</l>
<l>a)mi\s me/n, h)\n ou)rhtia/sh|s, au(thi\</l>
<l>para/ soi kremh/set' e)ggu\s e)pi\ tou= patta/lou.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>sofo/n ge touti\ kai\ ge/ronti pro/sforon</l>
<l n="810">e)chu=res a)texnw=s fa/rmakon straggouri/as.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>kai\ pu=r ge touti/: kai\ prose/sthken fakh=</l>
<l>r(ofei=n, e)a\n de/h| ti.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">tou=t' au)= decio/n:</l>
<l>ka)\n ga\r pure/ttw, to/n ge misqo\n lh/yomai.</l>
<l>au)tou= me/nwn ga\r th\n fakh=n r(ofh/somai.</l>
<l n="815">a)ta\r ti/ to\n o)/rnin w(s e)/m' e)chne/gkate;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>i(/na g', h)\n kaqeu/dh|s a)pologoume/nou tino/s,</l>
<l>a)/|dwn a)/nwqen e)cegei/rh| s' ou(tosi/.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>e(\n e)/ti poqw=, ta\ d' a)/ll' a)re/skei moi.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">to\ ti/;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>qh)rw=|on ei)/ pws e)kkomi/sais to\ tou= *lu/kou.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l n="820">pa/resti touti/, kau)to\s a(/nac ou(tosi/.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>w)= de/spoq' h(/rws w(s xalepo\s a)/r' h)=sq' i)dei=n.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>oi(=o/sper h(mi=n fai/netai *klew/numos.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>ou)/koun e)/xei g' ou)d' au)to\s h(/rws w)\n o(/pla.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>ei) qa=tton e)kaqi/zou su/, qa=tton a)\n di/khn</l>
<l n="825">e)ka/loun.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">ka/lei nun, w(s ka/qhmai 'gw\ pa/lai.<milestone ed="p" n="826" unit="card"/></l>
</sp>
<sp>
