<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">mhdamw=s tou=to/n g', e)pei\</l>
<l n="1165">pa/nu misola/kwn au)tou= 'stin ei(=s tw=n daktu/lwn.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>ou)k e)/sti para\ tau=t' a)/lla.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">kakodai/mwn e)gw/,</l>
<l>o(/stis e)pi\ gh/rws xi/metlon ou)de\n lh/yomai.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>a)/nuso/n poq' u(podhsa/menos: ei)=ta plousi/ws</l>
<l>w(di\ proba\s trufero/n ti diasalakw/nison.<milestone ed="p" n="1170" unit="card"/></l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l n="1170">i)dou/. qew= to\ sxh=ma, kai\ ske/yai m' o(/tw|</l>
<l>ma/list' e)/oika th\n ba/disin tw=n plousi/wn.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>o(/tw|; *doqih=ni sko/rodon h)mfiesme/nw|.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>kai\ mh\n proqumou=mai/ ge sauloprwktia=n.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>a)/ge nun, e)pisth/sei lo/gous semnou\s le/gein</l>
<l n="1175">a)ndrw=n paro/ntwn polumaqw=n kai\ deciw=n;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>e)/gwge.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">ti/na dh=t' a)\n le/gois;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">pollou\s pa/nu.</l>
<l>prw=ton me\n w(s h( *la/mi' a(lou=s' e)pe/rdeto,</l>
<l>e)/peita d' w(s o( *kardopi/wn th\n mhte/ra.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>mh/ 'moi/ ge mu/qous, a)lla\ tw=n a)nqrwpi/nwn,</l>
<l n="1180">oi(/ous le/gomen ma/lista tou\s kat' oi)ki/an.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>e)gw)=|da toi/nun tw=n ge pa/nu kat' oi)ki/an</l>
<l>e)kei=non w(s <q>ou(/tw pot' h)=n mu=s kai\ galh=.</q></l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>w)= skaie\ ka)pai/deute, *qeoge/nhs e)/fh</l>
<l>tw=| koprolo/gw| kai\ tau=ta loidorou/menos,</l>
<l n="1185">mu=s kai\ gala=s me/lleis le/gein e)n a)ndra/sin;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>poi/ous tina\s de\ xrh\ le/gein;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">megaloprepei=s,</l>
<l>w(s cuneqew/reis *)androklei= kai\ *kleisqe/nei.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>e)gw\ de\ teqew/rhka pow/pot' ou)damoi=</l>
<l>plh\n e)s *pa/ron, kai\ tau=ta du)/ o)bolw\ fe/rwn.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l n="1190">a)ll' ou)=n le/gein xrh/ s' w(s e)ma/xeto/ g' au)ti/ka</l>
<l>*)efoudi/wn pagkra/tion *)askw/nda| kalw=s,</l>
<l>h)/dh ge/rwn w)\n kai\ polio/s, e)/xwn de/ toi</l>
<l>pleura\n baquta/thn kai\ xe/ras kai\ lago/na kai\</l>
<l>qw/rak' a)/riston.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">pau=e pau=', ou)de\n le/geis.</l>
<l n="1195">pw=s a)\n maxe/saito pagkra/tion qw/rak' e)/xwn;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>ou(/tw dihgei=sqai nomi/zous' oi( sofoi/.</l>
<l>a)ll' e(/teron ei)pe/ moi: par' a)ndra/si ce/nois</l>
<l>pi/nwn seautou= poi=on a)\n le/cai dokei=s</l>
<l>e)pi\ neo/thtos e)/rgon a)ndrikw/taton;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l n="1200">e)kei=n' e)kei=n' a)ndreio/tato/n ge tw=n e)mw=n,</l>
<l>o(/t' *)ergasi/wnos ta\s xa/rakas u(feilo/mhn.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>a)polei=s me. poi/as xa/rakas; a)ll' w(s h)\ ka/pron</l>
<l>e)diw/kaqe/s pot' h)\ lagw/n, h)\ lampa/da</l>
<l>e)/drames, a)neurw\n o(/ ti neanikw/taton.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l n="1205">e)gw)=|da toi/nun to/ ge neanikw/taton:</l>
<l>o(/te to\n drome/a *fa/ullon w)\n bou/pais e)/ti</l>
<l>ei)=lon diw/kwn loidori/as yh/foin duoi=n.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>pau)=: a)lla\ deuri\ kataklinei\s prosma/nqane</l>
<l>cumpotiko\s ei)=nai kai\ cunousiastiko/s.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l n="1210">pw=s ou)=n kataklinw=; fra/z' a)nu/sas.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">eu)sxhmo/nws.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>w(di\ keleu/eis kataklinh=nai;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">mhdamw=s.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>pw=s dai/;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">ta\ go/nat' e)/kteine kai\ gumnastikw=s</l>
<l>u(gro\n xu/tlason seauto\n e)n toi=s strw/masin.</l>
<l>e)/peit' e)pai/neso/n ti tw=n xalkwma/twn,</l>
<l n="1215">o)rofh\n qe/asai, kreka/di' au)lh=s qau/mason:</l>
<l>u(/dwr kata\ xeiro/s: ta\s trape/zas e)sfe/rein:</l>
<l>deipnou=men: a)poneni/mmeq': h)/dh spe/ndomen.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>pro\s tw=n qew=n e)nu/pnion e(stiw/meqa;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>au(lhtri\s e)nefu/shsen: oi( de\ sumpo/tai</l>
<l n="1220">ei)si\n *qe/wros *ai)sxi/nhs *fa=nos *kle/wn,</l>
<l>ce/nos tis e(/teros pro\s kefalh=s *)ake/storos.</l>
<l>tou/tois cunw\n ta\ sko/li' o(/pws de/cei kalw=s.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>a)/lhqes; w(s ou)dei\s *diakri/wn de/cetai.<milestone ed="p" n="1224" unit="card"/></l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>e)gw\ ei)/somai: kai\ dh\ ga/r ei)m' e)gw\ *kle/wn,</l>
<l n="1225">a)/|dw de\ prw=tos *(armodi/ou: de/cai de\ su/.</l>
<l><q>ou)dei\s pw/pot' a)nh\r e)/gent' *)aqh/nais</q>&mdash;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>ou)x ou(/tw ge panou=rgos <add>ou)de\</add> kle/pths.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>touti\ su\ dra/seis; parapolei= bow/menos:</l>
<l>fh/sei ga\r e)colei=n se kai\ diafqerei=n</l>
<l n="1230">kai\ th=sde th=s gh=s e)cela=n.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">e)gw\ de/ ge,</l>
<l>e)a\n a)peilh=|, nh\ *di/' e(/ter' a)nta/|somai:</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>&lsquo;w)=nqrwf', ou)=tos o( maio/menos to\ me/ga kra/tos,</l>
<l n="1235">a)ntre/yeis e)/ti ta\n po/lin: a( d' e)/xetai r(opa=s.&rsquo;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>ti/ d' o(/tan *qe/wros pro\s podw=n katakei/menos</l>
<l>a)/|dh| *kle/wnos labo/menos th=s decia=s:</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l><q>*)admh/tou lo/gon w)=tai=re maqw\n tou\s a)gaqou\s fi/lei.</q></l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l n="1240">tou/tw| ti/ le/ceis sko/lion;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">w)|dikw=s e)gw/.</l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>&lsquo;ou)k e)/stin a)lwpeki/zein,</l>
<l>ou)d' a)mfote/roisi gi/gnesqai fi/lon.&rsquo;</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>meta\ tou=ton *ai)sxi/nhs o( *se/llou de/cetai,</l>
<l>a)uh\r sofo\s kai\ mousiko/s, ka)=|t' a)/|setai:</l>
</sp>
<div2 type="lyric">
<sp><speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l n="1245">&lsquo;xrh/mata kai\ bi/an</l>
<l>*kleitago/ra| te ka)moi\</l>
<l>meta\ *qettalw=n&rsquo;&mdash;</l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="lyric">
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>polla\ dh\ dieko/mpasas su\ ka)gw/.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>touti\ me\n e)pieikw=s su/ g' e)cepi/stasai:</l>
<l n="1250">o(/pws d' e)pi\ dei=pnon e)s *filokth/monos i)/men.</l>
<l>pai= pai=, to\ dei=pnon *xruse\ suskeu/aze nw=|n,</l>
<l>i(/na kai\ mequsqw=men dia\ xro/nou.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l part="M">mhdamw=s.</l>
<l>kako\n to\ pi/nein: a)po\ ga\r oi)/nou gi/gnetai</l>
<l>kai\ qurokoph=sai kai\ pata/cai kai\ balei=n,</l>
<l n="1255">ka)/peit' a)poti/nein a)rgu/rion e)k kraipa/lhs.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>ou)/k, h)\n cunh=|s g' a)ndra/si kaloi=s te ka)gaqoi=s.</l>
<l>h)\ ga\r parh|th/santo to\n peponqo/ta,</l>
<l>h)\ lo/gon e)/lecas au)to\s a)stei=o/n tina,</l>
<l>*ai)swpiko\n ge/loion h)\ *subaritiko/n,</l>
<l n="1260">w(=n e)/maqes e)n tw=| sumposi/w|: ka)=|t' e)s ge/lwn</l>
<l>to\ pra=gm' e)/treyas, w(/st' a)fei/s s' a)poixetai.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>maqhte/on ta)/r' e)sti\ pollou\s tw=n lo/gwn,</l>
<l>ei)/per a)potei/sw mhde/n, h)/n ti drw= kako/n.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*bdelukle/wn</speaker>
<l>a)/ge nun i)/wmen: mhde\n h(ma=s i)sxe/tw.<milestone ed="p" n="1265" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2></div1>
<div1 type="Choral">
<div2 type="strophe">
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l n="1265">polla/kis dh\ 'doc' e)mautw=| deceio\s pefuke/nai</l>
<l>kai\ skaio\s ou)depw/pote:</l>
<l>a)ll' *)amuni/as o( *se/llou ma=llon ou(k tw=n *krwbu/lwn,</l>
<l>ou(=tos o(/n g' e)gw/ pot' ei)=don a)nti\ mh/lou kai\ r(oa=s</l>
<l>deipnou=nta meta\ *lewgo/rou:</l>
<l n="1270">peinh=| ga\r h(=|per *)antifw=n:</l>
<l>a)lla\ presbeu/wn ga\r e)s *fa/rsalon w)/|xet', ei)=t' e)kei=</l>
<l>mo/nos mo/nois</l>
<l>toi=s *pene/staisi cunh=n toi=s</l>
<l>*qettalw=n, au)to\s pene/sths w)\n e)/lattwn ou)deno/s.<milestone ed="p" n="1275" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="epirrheme"> <!-- AEM:  was marked as "lyric" -->
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l n="1275">w)= maka/ri' *au)to/menes w(/s se makari/zomen,</l>
<l>pai=das e)fu/teusas o(/ti xeirotexnikwta/tous:</l>
<l>prw=ta me\n a(/pasi fi/lon a)/ndra te sofw/taton,</l>
<l>to\n kifaraoido/taton, w(=| xa/ris e)fe/speto:</l>
<l>to\n d' u(pokrith\n e(/teron a)rgale/on w(s sofo/n:</l>
<l n="1280">ei)=t' *)arifra/dhn polu/ ti qumosofikw/taton,</l>
<l>o(/ntina/ pot' w)/mose maqo/nta para\ mhdeno/s,</l>
<l>a)ll' a)po\ sofh=s fu/seos au)to/maton e)kmaqei=n</l>
<l>glwttopoiei=n e)s ta\ pornei=' ei)sio/nq' e(ka/stote.<milestone ed="p" n="1284" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="antistrophe">
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l><gap desc="*"/></l>
</sp></div2>
<div2 type="antepirrheme">
<sp><speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>ei)si/ tines oi(/ m' e)/legon w(s katadihlla/ghn,</l>
<l n="1285">h(ni/ka *kle/wn m' u(peta/ratten e)pikei/menos</l>
<l>&dagger; kai/ me kaki/stais &dagger; e)/knise: ka)=|q' o(/t' a)pedeiro/mhn,</l>
<l>ou(kto\s e)ge/lwn me/ga kekrago/ta qew/menoi,</l>
<l>ou)de\n a)/r' e)mou= me/lon, o(/son de\ mo/non ei)de/nai</l>
<l>skwmma/tion ei)/pote/ ti qlibo/menos e)kbalw=.</l>
<l n="1290">tau=ta katidw\n u(po/ ti mikro\n e)piqh/kisa:</l>
<l>ei)=ta nu=n e)chpa/thsen h( xa/rac th\n a)/mpelon.<milestone ed="p" n="1292" unit="card"/></l>
</sp></div2></div1>
<div1 type="Episode">
<sp><speaker>*canqi/as</speaker>
<l>i)w\ xelw=nai maka/riai tou= de/rmatos,</l>
<l>kai\ tri\s maka/riai tou= 'pi\ tai=s pleurai=s te/gous.</l>
<l>w(s eu)= kathre/yasqe kai\ noubustikw=s</l>
<l n="1295">kera/mw| to\ nw=ton w(/ste ta\s plhga\s ste/gein.</l>
<l>e)gw\ d' a)po/lwla stizo/menos bakthri/a|.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*xoro/s</speaker>
<l>ti/ d' e)/stin w)= pai=; pai=da ga/r, ka)\n h)=| ge/rwn,</l>
<l>kalei=n di/kaion o(/stis a)\n plhga\s la/bh|.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*canqi/as</speaker>
<l>ou) ga\r o( ge/rwn a)thro/taton a)/r' h)=n kako\n</l>
<l n="1300">kai\ tw=n cuno/ntwn polu\ paroinikw/tatos;</l>
<l>kai/toi parh=n *(/ippullos *)antifw=n *lu/kwn</l>
<l>*lusi/stratos *qou/frastos oi( peri\ *fru/nixon.</l>
<l>tou/twn a(pa/ntwn h)=n u(bristo/tatos makrw=|.</l>
<l>eu)qu\s ga\r w(s e)ne/plhto pollw=n ka)gaqw=n,</l>
<l n="1305">e)nh/lat' e)ski/rta 'pepo/rdei katege/la</l>
<l>w(/sper kaxru/wn o)ni/dion eu)wxhme/non</l>
<l>ka)/tupten e)me\ neanikw=s <q>pai= pai=</q> kalw=n.</l>
<l>ei)=t' au)to\n w(s ei)=d' h)/|kasen *lusi/stratos:</l>
<l>&lsquo;e)/oikas w)= presbu=ta neoplou/tw| trugi\</l>
<l n="1310">klhth=ri/ t' ei)s a)xurmo\n a)podedrako/ti.&rsquo;</l>
<l>o( d' a)nakragw\n a)nth/|kas' au)to\n pa/rnopi</l>
<l>ta\ qri=a tou= tri/bwnos a)pobeblhko/ti,</l>
<l>*sqene/lw| te ta\ skeua/ria diakekarme/nw|.</l>
<l>oi( d' a)nekro/thsan, plh/n ge *qoufra/stou mo/nou:</l>
<l n="1315">ou(=tos de\ diemu/llainen w(s dh\ decio/s.</l>
<l>o( ge/rwn de\ to\n *qou/fraston h)/ret': 'ei)pe/ moi,</l>
<l>e)pi\ tw=| koma=|s kai\ komyo\s ei)=nai prospoiei=,</l>
<l>kwmw|doloixw=n peri\ to\n eu)= pra/ttont' a)ei/;'</l>
<l>toiau=ta periu/brizen au)tou\s e)n me/rei,</l>
<l n="1320">skw/ptwn a)groi/kws kai\ prose/ti lo/gous le/gwn</l>
<l>a)maqe/stat' ou)de\n ei)ko/tas tw=| pra/gmati.</l>
<l>e)/peit' e)peidh\ 'me/quen, oi)/kad' e)/rxetai</l>
<l>tu/ptwn a(/pantas, h)/n tis au)tw=| cuntu/xh|.</l>
<l>o(di\ de\ kai\ dh\ sfallo/menos prose/rxetai.</l>
<l n="1325">a)ll' e)kpodw\n a)/peimi pri\n plhga\s labei=n.<milestone ed="p" n="1326" unit="card"/></l>
</sp>
<div2 type="lyric">
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l>a)/nexe pa/rexe:</l>
<l>klau/setai/ tis tw=n o)/pisqen</l>
<l>e)pakolouqou/ntwn e)moi/:</l>
<l>oi(=on, ei) mh\ 'rrh/seq', u(ma=s</l>
<l n="1330">w)= po/nhroi tauth|i\ th=|</l>
<l>da|di\ fruktou\s skeua/sw.</l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*cumo/ths tis</speaker>
<l>h)= mh\n su\ dw/seis au)/rion tou/twn di/khn</l>
<l>h(mi=n a(/pasi, kei) sfo/dr' ei)= neani/as.</l>
<l>a(qro/oi ga\r h(/come/n se proskalou/menoi.<milestone ed="p" n="1335" unit="card"/></l>
</sp>
<sp>
<speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>
<l n="1335">i)h\ i)eu=, kalou/menoi.</l>
<l>a)rxai=a/ g' u(mw=n: a)=ra/ g' i)/sq'</l>
<l>w(s ou)d' a)kou/wn a)ne/xomai</l>
<l>dikw=n; i)aiboi=, ai)boi=.</l>
<l>ta/de m' a)re/skei: ba/lle khmou/s.</l>
<l n="1340">ou)k a)/peisi; pou= 'stin <add>h(mi=n</add></l>
<l>h(liasth/s; e)kpodw/n.<milestone ed="p" n="1342" unit="card"/></l>
</sp>
<sp><speaker>*filokle/wn</speaker>  <!-- AEM:  why another speech tag here? -->
<l>a)na/baine deu=ro xrusomhlolo/nqion,</l>
<l>th=| xeiri\ toudi\ labome/nh tou= sxoini/ou.</l>
<l>e)/xou: fula/ttou d', w(s sapro\n to\ sxoini/on:</l>
<l>o(/mws ge me/ntoi tribo/menon ou)k a)/xqetai.</l>
<l n="1345">o(ra=|s e)gw/ s' w(s deciw=s u(feilo/mhn</l>
<l>me/llousan h)/dh lesbia=n tou\s cumpo/tas:</l>
<l>w(=n ou(/nek' a)po/dos tw=| pe/ei tw|di\ xa/rin.</l>
<l>a)ll' ou)k a)podw/seis ou)d' e)fialei=s oi)=d' o(/ti,</l>
