<l>nu=n d' ou) kratw= 'gw\ tw=n e)mautou= xrhma/twn</l>
<l n="1355">ne/os ga/r ei)mi kai\ fula/ttomai sfo/dra.</l>
<l>to\ ga\r ui(/dion threi= me, ka)/sti du/skolon</l>
